{"tid":2283731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[旅遊氣泡] 李顯龍：示威者「五大訴求」旨在推翻香港政府","createTime":"2020-11-12T20:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T17:08:41.000Z","uid":312206,"like":75,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"272fdd752a42106b4804a6744f84c76c40d87e77","tid":2283731,"uid":312206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:18:50.000Z","msg":"先唔好講近排又多返個案個氣泡會唔會爆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算唔爆，香港人都無可能若無其事咁去新加坡送錢比佢地，留返係香港洗錢，撐返自己人唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我地一齊回下帶，睇下你仲想唔想送錢比佢地洗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍：示威者「五大訴求」旨在推翻香港政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcd.com/content/2019-10/17/content_1160548.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fcontent%2F2019-10%2F17%2Fcontent_1160548.html&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Bymvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=395da872\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcd.com/content/2019-10/17/content_1160548.html</a><br />\n<br />\n新加坡內務部部長：港示威更顯星嚴格是正確 國際媒體只針對香港警察 香港示威者攻擊警察及民居<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ir-basilica.com/新加坡內務部部長：港示威更顯星嚴格是正確-國際/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ir-basilica.com%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%85%A7%E5%8B%99%E9%83%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%9B%B4%E9%A1%AF%E6%98%9F%E5%9A%B4%E6%A0%BC%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Bymvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=803dc9a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ir-basilica.com/新加坡內務部部長：港示威更顯星嚴格是正確-國際/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍妻力挺香港警察？何晶個人臉書轉香港撐警貼文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/124346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Famparticle%2F124346&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Bymvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=99a08c4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/124346</a><br />\n<br />\n何晶再分享台灣新聞 網友「Errr」了：高級酸啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.chinatimes.com/amp/realtimenews/20200414002587-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Famp%2Frealtimenews%2F20200414002587-260407&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Bymvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=1f6cdbb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.chinatimes.com/amp/realtimenews/20200414002587-260407</a><br />\n<br />\nSingapore &lsquo;idiot&rsquo;s guide&rsquo; to coronavirus crisis control: don&rsquo;t do it like Hong Kong<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3051916/singapore-idiots-guide-coronavirus-crisis-control-dont-do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3051916%2Fsingapore-idiots-guide-coronavirus-crisis-control-dont-do&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Bymvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=6c7edeb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3051916/singapore-idiots-guide-coronavirus-crisis-control-dont-do</a><br />\n<br />\nSingapore minister Chan Chun Sing mocked for saying cotton comes from sheep<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.scmp.com/news/asia/southeast-asia/article/3087040/singapore-minister-chan-chun-sing-mocked-saying-cotton\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fasia%2Fsoutheast-asia%2Farticle%2F3087040%2Fsingapore-minister-chan-chun-sing-mocked-saying-cotton&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Bymvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=9a67c955\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.scmp.com/news/asia/southeast-asia/article/3087040/singapore-minister-chan-chun-sing-mocked-saying-cotton</a><br />\n<br />\n唔想睇字？ 又得姐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2655000/2659441/874814_600.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2655000%2F2659441%2F874814_600.PNG&h=c4db6394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/1008/U633P22DT20191008173102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F1008%2FU633P22DT20191008173102.jpg&h=48e85a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/201910/20191020/Cartoon20191026.jpg?itok=6a8OYvhJ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com.sg%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle_large_full%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F201910%2F20191020%2FCartoon20191026.jpg%3Fitok%3D6a8OYvhJ&h=7e87956f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d5bc52/f/800x0/https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7tRPaXBouQU/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fd5bc52%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F7tRPaXBouQU%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=6fb75d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁當然啦，除左上面罄竹難書嘅罪狀之外，香港本身都有好多嘢優勝過佢地嘅。<br />\n<br />\n成日拎自己同我地比，其實我地從來無放過你喺眼內。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨係香港嘅文化歷史都贏佢地九條街啦。<br />\n睇下套Crazy Rich Asian就見到新加坡根本就冇自己嘅文化內涵可以 sale。<br />\n<br />\n香港呢？電影，動畫，漫畫，甚至英劇都會有係香港取景，又有自己嘅語言，好過佢哋十尻幾倍啦。<br />\n<br />\n好似講遠左，不過總之我就唔會去資源敵人㗎勒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n射落海都唔益坡狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁耐無飛，邊到都殺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de66396c9f2087c0b0210abf8575ba45137f1cf","tid":2283731,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:23:45.000Z","msg":"🙈🙈🙈<br />\n佢哋係衰嘅<br />\n不過真係想去旅行咁點？"},{"pid":"e54ad6ba814a0a2954b87b61434a32623f0c943e","tid":2283731,"uid":6532,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:26:36.000Z","msg":"港豬睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b24ad35697ce78245ee2050097ca702c98d827","tid":2283731,"uid":312206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6de66396c9f2087c0b0210abf8575ba45137f1cf","tid":2283731,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:23:45.000Z","msg":"🙈🙈🙈<br />\n佢哋係衰嘅<br />\n不過真係想去旅行咁點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:28:42.000Z","msg":"探索下本地旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81c638f7e8b4532c37987ed7721e92d5ff6c14f","tid":2283731,"uid":280044,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:29:05.000Z","msg":"講真新加坡好悶<br />\n去過一次之後已經冇意欲再去<br />\n洗費又唔係平<br />\n留返d錢遲d去日本去過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01a9606de523d9b0095881aed72916a42229b66","tid":2283731,"uid":78302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:29:33.000Z","msg":"去新加坡把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812ec403e14abb2d91cb71829d4826c74bb71794","tid":2283731,"uid":312206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e54ad6ba814a0a2954b87b61434a32623f0c943e","tid":2283731,"uid":6532,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:26:36.000Z","msg":"港豬睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:29:56.000Z","msg":"又唔好咁講 有時都要提下佢地嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提完都要去就⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94f34f3204afc51a51307f47bdac1a43dd3d728","tid":2283731,"uid":312206,"like":2,"dislike":0,